    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single mark on it, and the interior is still smelling fresh. It drives like an absolute dream, and I\u2019m only letting it go because I need something a bit bigger for the family. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, come say hi and take it for a spin!",
