    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving German engineering, featuring the S65 4.0L V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. The vehicle exhibits exceptional mechanical integrity; the throttle actuators and rod bearings have been serviced preventatively to ensure peak longitudinal performance. Its Alpine White finish remains factory-correct with no evidence of oxidation or clear coat failure. The cabin is equally impressive, with the Novillo leather bolsters showing no compression or wear. Equipped with Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and a factory carbon fiber roof to lower the center of gravity, this chassis remains as rigid and responsive as the day it left Regensburg. A turn-key investment for the serious driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
